change are shown in the preceding table. The increase in rates and pricing was primarily due to an increase in revenues related to
the recovery of Plant Vogtle Units 3 and 4 construction financing costs under the NCCR tariff. See Note 2 to the financial
statements under "Georgia Power – Nuclear Construction – Regulatory Matters" for additional information on the NCCR tariff.
