$23 million of additional amortization of intangible assets as a result of fair value adjustments in acquisition accounting, primarily
at gas marketing services, as well as depreciation at gas distribution operations due to continued investment in infrastructure
programs.
For the predecessor period of January 1, 2016 through June 30, 2016, depreciation and amortization was $206 million and reflected
depreciation related to additional assets placed in service at gas distribution operations due to continued investment in infrastructure
programs.
