For the successor year ended December 31, 2018, a goodwill impairment charge of $42 million was recorded in contemplation of
the sale of Pivotal Home Solutions. See Notes 1 and 15 to the financial statements under "Goodwill and Other Intangible Assets
and Liabilities" and "Southern Company Gas – Sale of Pivotal Home Solutions," respectively, for additional information.
