EBIT and adjusted operating margin should not be considered alternatives to, or more meaningful indicators of, Southern Company
Gas' operating performance than net income attributable to Southern Company Gas or operating income as determined in
accordance with GAAP. In addition, Southern Company Gas' adjusted operating margin may not be comparable to similarly titled
measures of other companies.
Detailed variance explanations of Southern Company Gas' financial performance are provided herein.
