contractor litigation claims. Interest expense reflects the impact of intercompany promissory notes executed in December 2016 and
the issuance of first mortgage bonds at Nicor Gas in August 2017 and November 2017. Income tax expense includes a $22 million
benefit as a result of the Tax Reform Legislation.
