liable for the obligations incurred under these agreements. See Note 9 under "Fuel and Power Purchase Agreements" for additional
information. Southern Power and the traditional electric operating companies generally settle amounts related to the above
transactions on a monthly basis in the month following the performance of such services or the purchase or sale of electricity. See
