Southern Company. In addition to these items, Southern Company's goodwill and other intangible assets also relate to its 2016
acquisition of PowerSecure. See Note 15 under "Southern Company Merger with Southern Company Gas" and "Southern
Company Acquisition of PowerSecure" for additional information.
