commodity purchases associated with Southern Company Gas' gas marketing services of 47 million mmBtu at floating gas prices
calculated using forward natural gas prices at December 31, 2018 and valued at $150 million. Southern Company Gas provides
guarantees to certain gas suppliers for certain of its subsidiaries in support of payment obligations.
