Southern Company Gas' Results of Operations and Pro Forma Financial Information
The results of operations for Southern Company Gas have been included in Southern Company's consolidated financial statements
from the date of acquisition and consisted of operating revenues of $1.7 billion and net income of $114 million in 2016.
The following summarized unaudited pro forma consolidated statement of earnings information assumes that the acquisition of
Southern Company Gas was completed on January 1, 2015. The summarized unaudited pro forma consolidated statement of
earnings information includes adjustments for (i) intercompany sales, (ii) amortization of intangible assets, (iii) adjustments to
interest expense to reflect current interest rates on Southern Company Gas debt and additional interest expense associated with
borrowings by Southern Company to fund the Merger, and (iv) the elimination of nonrecurring expenses associated with the
Merger.
